dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature dataset within the geodatabase Sauk_Zoning_2016. The features included in this feature dataset are 'AIRPORT', 'FARMLAND', 'FLOODPLAIN', 'GENERAL', and 'SHORELAND'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://saukgis.maps.arcgis.com/home/index.html
